      <t>This document describes a framework for providing multicast as a
   service via Bit Index Explicit Replication (BIER) [RFC7279], and
   specifies a few enhancements to [draft-ietf-bier-idr-extensions]
   [RFC8279] [RFC8401] [RFC8444] to enable multicast/BIER as a service.</t>
